down and what to let go.

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:28.680 align:middle line:90%
>> When to fold them.

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:28.990 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:05:28.990 --> 00:05:29.300 align:middle line:90%
>> That's right.

00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:30.967 align:middle line:84%
When to hold them and
when to fold them.

00:05:30.967 --> 00:05:33.320 align:middle line:84%
>> You've said, also, that
