00:07:19.210 --> 00:07:25.090 align:middle line:84%
Now, the wonderful thing is that
in the evolutionary process,

00:07:25.090 --> 00:07:29.980 align:middle line:84%
we are learning
that we can learn,

00:07:29.980 --> 00:07:34.442 align:middle line:84%
discover with less and less
