00:07:34.442 --> 00:07:35.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, with self-awareness.

00:07:35.650 --> 00:07:36.130 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:07:36.130 --> 00:07:36.590 align:middle line:90%
That's right.

00:07:36.590 --> 00:07:36.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:07:36.950 --> 00:07:38.080 align:middle line:90%
>> That's the good news.

00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:42.930 align:middle line:84%
