00:08:09.340 --> 00:08:10.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:08:10.390 --> 00:08:14.620 align:middle line:84%
And we are learning how to make
better choices, definitely,

00:08:14.620 --> 00:08:17.170 align:middle line:90%
